lead_paragraph: Kansas prosecutors declined to bring felony charges against Randle in a case related to a report of a domestic disturbance at a hotel in Wichita on Feb. 3.

headline.print_headline: Cowboys’ Randle Will Not Face Felony Charges
headline.main: Cowboys’ Joseph Randle Will Not Face Felony Charges

snippet: Kansas prosecutors declined to bring felony charges against Randle in a case related to a report of a domestic disturbance at a hotel in Wichita on Feb. 3.
abstract: Dallas Cowboys running back Joseph Randle will not face felony charges in Kansas after domestic disturbance report.
